text: Rodrigo Díaz (born 16 November 1978) is a Colombian equestrian. He competed in the individual jumping event at the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Colombian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Colombia Category:Equestrians at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2011 Pan American Games Category:Sportspeople from Bogotá
